Bro, I've got a plan.

20
00:02:44,420 --> 00:02:45,680
Did you hear the news?

21
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:47,440
What is it? What news?

22
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:49,880
They said it will rain for 30 consecutive days.

23
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,880
You're not going to ask me about my plan?

24
00:02:52,300 --> 00:02:54,300
Fine. What is your plan?

25
00:02:54,420 --> 00:02:59,180
If it rains heavily, I won't be able to go out to deliver. Why don't we start selling umbrellas instead?

26
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,860
