27
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,620
From your store.

28
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:10,720
Most of the people might want to get wet in the rain.

29
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,300
They won't buy umbrellas.

30
00:03:12,940 --> 00:03:13,620
Really?

31
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,560
Single people looking for their soulmates,

32
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:21,060
they'll dash into the rain!

33
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,460
I'm so jealous of those people

34
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,100
who can see their soulmates in the rain.

35
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:29,640
Oh, right.

36
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:33,180
You're soulmate blind.

37
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,820
You don't have to repeat that.

38
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,740
I'm sorry.

39
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,540
But really,

40
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:46,060
who would be crazy enough to run into the rain just to see their soulmate?

41
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:48,360
They'll just end up with pneumonia instead.

42
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:51,020
Exactly!

43
00:03:52,020 --> 00:03:54,020
So what do you think? Are you in?

44
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,500
I can't go to sell umbrellas with you.

45
00:03:57,220 --> 00:03:58,540
I have to look after this store.

46
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:01,300
How about this?

47
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:02,880
You can stay here.

48
00:04:03,220 --> 00:04:04,480
And I'll go out there to sell them.

49
00:04:04,620 --> 00:04:06,280
And we can share the profits, seventy-thirty.

50
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,820
Are you crazy?

51
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,020
Sixty-fourty.

52
00:04:09,140 --> 00:04:11,540
Come on, bro!

53
00:04:11,540 --> 00:04:13,340
Sixty-five to thirty-five. No more negotiation. The deal is done.

54
00:04:15,260 --> 00:04:16,940
Fine. You win again.

55
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:20,180
I'll go get the umbrellas then.

56
00:04:20,180 --> 00:04:20,960
Okay.

57
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:27,320
Whoa.

58
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:29,660
Are you crazy?

59
00:04:29,820 --> 00:04:30,560
I'm off!

60
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:31,540
What!

61
00:04:31,620 --> 00:04:32,320
You should pay first.

62
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:36,260
Add it to my bill. I'll come back to pay later. I'm leaving. Bye!

63
00:04:36,260 --> 00:04:37,840
Gosh!

64
00:04:38,340 --> 00:04:39,600
Clumsy as always.

65
00:04:39,780 --> 00:04:41,440
