290
00:20:00,360 --> 00:20:01,460
I can use the app.

291
00:20:01,560 --> 00:20:02,460
Come on.

292
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:11,520
You see? I can drop you off here, and it’s all free.

293
00:20:13,660 --> 00:20:14,380
Yeah.

294
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:15,980
Thank you.

295
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:21,380
By the way, if your office needs a messenger, feel free to contact me.

296
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:23,900
Or if you need someone to take you anywhere and drop you off, just call me.

297
00:20:23,900 --> 00:20:25,900
